data.description: Come see your new home today! This property is located in the well established Montclair subdivision which is close to shopping and dining. This home includes an INGROUND POOL with a pool pump timer, LED lights, internet throughout the living areas and is currently finishing up with renovations that include new carpet and freshly painted walls. Also, your future home comes with a driveway that extends into the backyard (perfect for guest and pool events ) Schedule your appointment now!!!!!!!!
